text: King Creek may refer to: * King Creek, Ontario, Canada, a community in the township of King * Kings Creek, South Carolina, USA ** King's Creek Furnace Site (38CK71), an historic site in the South Carolina community * King Creek (Crow River), a stream in Minnesota * A stream in Tishomingo, Mississippi, USA * An area in Wauchope, New South Wales, Australia * A location on Route B of NORAD's Ballistic Missile Early Warning System Rearward Communications System == See also == * King River (disambiguation) * King (disambiguation) * Kings Creek (disambiguation)
